highlights.text: “Love Always Run Away” by Lim Young Woong has been on Top Songs South Korea the longest, at 1364 days straight.
Lim Young Woong has the most spots on Top Songs South Korea. “Heavenly Ever After” is the highest at #25.
“OPENING” by 고추잠자리 is the biggest gainer on Top Songs South Korea, up 80 spots at #64.
“LOVE ME” by Zion.T is the highest new entry on Top Songs South Korea at #164.
